---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "Freelance MERN Developer Ahmedabad | Nikhil";
const pageDescription = "Freelance full stack and AI developer in Ahmedabad. Build MERN platforms, agentic AI systems, and scalable digital products for business growth.";
const pageKeywords = "freelance MERN developer Ahmedabad, AI developer Ahmedabad, full stack developer Ahmedabad, agentic AI developer Gujarat";

const serviceSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
  serviceType: "MERN and AI Product Development",
  areaServed: "Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India",
  provider: {
    "@type": "Person",
    name: "Nikhil Yagik",
    url: "https://nikhilyagik.dev/developer-in-ahmedabad"
  },
  description: pageDescription
};
---

<MainLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} keywords={pageKeywords} image="/logo.png">
  <main class="bg-white min-h-screen pt-28 pb-20 px-4">
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-wide text-slate-500 uppercase mb-4">Ahmedabad Product Engineering</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-6">Freelance Full Stack and AI Developer in Ahmedabad</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Ahmedabad is one of the fastest-moving startup and business hubs in Gujarat, and product teams here need developers who can ship quickly without sacrificing architecture quality.
        I help businesses in Ahmedabad build conversion-focused web platforms, robust backend systems, and AI-enabled workflows that deliver measurable value.
        My specialization combines MERN stack engineering with practical AI system development, including agentic pipelines, retrieval workflows, and LLM application integration.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        If you are looking for a freelance MERN developer in Ahmedabad or an AI developer who can move from idea to production,
        I can support your team with ownership, speed, and technical clarity.
        I focus on business outcomes: better lead flow, faster operations, stronger user retention, and systems your team can actually maintain.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Full Stack and AI Services for Ahmedabad Businesses</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        My full stack work includes frontend architecture, backend API design, authentication systems,
        database modeling, deployment pipelines, and post-launch optimization.
        I build in React, Astro, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB, with a strong focus on scalability and maintainability.
        For companies with established products, I can also step in for feature expansion,
        workflow redesign, and system cleanup to improve delivery velocity.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        On the AI side, I build systems that are useful in real operations.
        This includes RAG-powered assistants for company knowledge, multi-step workflows in LangGraph,
        and AI integrations that support internal teams in support, content, and analysis use cases.
        The goal is not to bolt on AI for marketing language, but to integrate intelligence where it creates real business leverage.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2 mb-10">
        <li>MERN product development for startups and service companies</li>
        <li>Admin systems, role-based workflows, and API integrations</li>
        <li>Agentic AI architecture using LangGraph and tool orchestration</li>
        <li>RAG systems for searchable internal knowledge and documents</li>
        <li>Deployment, technical documentation, and growth-focused iteration</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Featured Work: Servielliance, TimeCapsule, and AI Delivery</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        Servielliance is a strong full stack example that reflects how I engineer for product depth.
        It includes role-based booking flows, lifecycle management, and scalable backend logic.
        This kind of architecture is ideal for Ahmedabad startups that need to grow without rewriting core systems every few months.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        TimeCapsule demonstrates how AI can be integrated into user-centered products.
        The platform allows users to manage scheduled reminders and stored messages through natural language,
        blending conventional product engineering with intelligent interaction design.
        This pattern is relevant for businesses that want better customer experience and internal efficiency through AI.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        I also build larger agentic systems, including LangGraph pipelines for planning, retrieval, and controlled output generation.
        These systems are useful when teams need repeatable workflows rather than one-time experiments.
        If your Ahmedabad business wants AI that performs tasks, not just chats,
        this implementation model is built for that goal.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Why Ahmedabad Clients Hire Me</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        Speed matters in Ahmedabad, but speed without structure creates expensive rework.
        My process balances fast execution with clear architecture decisions.
        I break delivery into milestones, align features to business priorities,
        and maintain documentation so your team can scale the system confidently.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        You also get single-point ownership across frontend, backend, and AI.
        That means fewer handoff issues, faster troubleshooting,
        and stronger alignment between product behavior and technical implementation.
        Instead of coordinating multiple specialists for every release,
        you can move forward with one accountable engineering partner.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        I work with founders, operators, and product teams who value clarity.
        You will always know current progress, next milestone, and expected outcomes.
        This is one of the key reasons long-term collaborations stay productive.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Lets Build in Ahmedabad</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        If you need a freelance full stack developer in Ahmedabad,
        or an AI developer in Gujarat who can build production-ready workflows,
        I am available for both short-term product launches and long-term roadmap execution.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        Share your product vision, timeline, and current bottlenecks.
        I will suggest a practical implementation path with clear scope and delivery phases.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions from Ahmedabad Teams</h2>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Can you work with startup founders who need quick MVP delivery?</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        Yes. I regularly work with founder-led teams that need fast MVP launches,
        investor demo readiness, and a codebase that can scale after validation.
        I prioritize core flows first, then expand the platform in controlled iterations,
        so your speed to market stays high without sacrificing architecture quality.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Do you handle both architecture and implementation?</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        Yes. I can own solution design, feature implementation, integration work,
        and deployment planning.
        This is especially useful for Ahmedabad businesses that want one accountable developer
        instead of coordinating multiple freelancers for every release.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Can AI be added to our current product roadmap?</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        Definitely. I can identify where AI creates immediate business value,
        such as retrieval-based assistance, intelligent workflow routing, or support automation.
        Then I integrate the AI layer into your existing system architecture,
        so you get practical outcomes rather than disconnected prototypes.
      </p>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Need a Developer in Ahmedabad?</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Lets plan your build with the right architecture, execution speed, and AI strategy from day one.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/#contact" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-900 text-white font-medium hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors">Hire Me</a>
          <a href="/#projects" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-900 font-medium hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors">View Work</a>
          <a href="/ai-developer-umbergaon" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-900 font-medium hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors">Umbergaon AI Page</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(serviceSchema)} />
</MainLayout>
